###################### adding leaders

@add_advisors
title: Add advisors
choose-if: n_advisors < 3
unavailable-subtitle: Maximum of 3 advisors.
go-to: advisor_menu

@advisor_menu
title: Add other advisors.
tags: radical_advisor, moderate_advisor, conservative_advisor, liberal_advisor, nonfactional_advisor
frequency: 1

- @Radical: Add Radical advisor
- @Moderate: Add Moderate advisor
- @Conservative: Add Conservative advisor
- @Liberal: Add Liberal advisor
- @Nonfactional: Add non-factional advisor
- @rm_main: Remove advisors instead.
- @remove_none: Stop changing advisors.

@Radical
view-if: n_advisors < 3

- #radical_advisor

@Moderate
view-if: n_advisors < 3

- #moderate_advisor

@Conservative
view-if: n_advisors < 3

- #conservative_advisor

@Liberal
view-if: n_advisors < 3

- #liberal_advisor

@Nonfactional
view-if: n_advisors < 3

- #nonfactional_advisor

###################### RADICAL ADVISORS

@add_stevens
title: Thaddeus Stevens
subtitle: Leader of the Radical Republicans in the House. Uncompromising champion of equality.
is-card: true
card-image: img/portraits/Thaddeus_Stevens.jpg
tags: radical_advisor
view-if: stevens_advisor = 0 and stevens_dead = 0 and n_advisors < 3
on-arrival: stevens_advisor = 1; n_advisors += 1; radical_strength += 3; radical_dissent -= 3
go-to: advisor_menu

Thaddeus Stevens is now an advisor.

@add_sumner
title: Charles Sumner
subtitle: Senate leader of the Radical Republicans. Passionate abolitionist and champion of Black civil rights.
is-card: true
card-image: img/portraits/Charles_Sumner.jpg
tags: radical_advisor
view-if: sumner_advisor = 0 and n_advisors < 3 and liberal_split = 0
on-arrival: sumner_advisor = 1; n_advisors += 1; radical_strength += 4; radical_dissent -= 4; freemen_rep += 2
go-to: advisor_menu

Charles Sumner is now an advisor. His moral authority on questions of equality is unmatched in the Senate.

@add_wade
title: Benjamin Wade
subtitle: Senate President Pro Tempore. Radical firebrand and potential president.
is-card: true
card-image: img/portraits/Benjamin_F_Wade.jpg
tags: radical_advisor
view-if: wade_advisor = 0 and n_advisors < 3 and president != "Wade"
on-arrival: wade_advisor = 1; n_advisors += 1; radical_strength += 3; radical_dissent -= 3; conservative_dissent += 2
go-to: advisor_menu

Benjamin Wade is now an advisor. His blunt radicalism energizes the party's left wing.

@add_chandler
title: Zachariah Chandler
subtitle: Michigan senator and aggressive Radical party organizer.
is-card: true
card-image: img/portraits/Zachariah_Chandler.jpg
tags: radical_advisor
view-if: chandler_advisor = 0 and n_advisors < 3
on-arrival: chandler_advisor = 1; n_advisors += 1; radical_strength += 3; radical_dissent -= 3
go-to: advisor_menu

Zachariah Chandler is now an advisor. He lacks Stevens's philosophical depth but more than compensates with organizational ferocity.

@add_morton
title: Oliver Morton
subtitle: Indiana governor and senator. One of the most powerful Radical party bosses in the country.
is-card: true
card-image: img/portraits/Oliver_Hazard_Perry_Morton.jpg
tags: radical_advisor
view-if: morton_advisor = 0 and n_advisors < 3
on-arrival: morton_advisor = 1; n_advisors += 1; radical_strength += 4; radical_dissent -= 3; IN_workers_rep += 3; IN_rural_rep += 2
go-to: advisor_menu

Oliver Morton is now an advisor. His iron grip on Indiana Republican politics is a significant asset.

@add_butler
title: Benjamin Butler
subtitle: Controversial Massachusetts Radical. Ruthless and effective.
is-card: true
card-image: img/portraits/Benjamin_Butler.jpg
tags: radical_advisor
view-if: butler_advisor = 0 and n_advisors < 3
on-arrival: butler_advisor = 1; n_advisors += 1; radical_strength += 3; radical_dissent -= 4; moderate_dissent += 3; liberal_dissent += 3
go-to: advisor_menu

Benjamin Butler is now an advisor. His methods are controversial but his results are hard to argue with.

###################### MODERATE ADVISORS

@add_garfield
title: James Garfield
subtitle: Ohio war hero and rising moderate star. Skilled master debater.
is-card: true
card-image: img/portraits/James_Abram_Garfield.jpg
tags: moderate_advisor
view-if: garfield_advisor = 0 and n_advisors < 3
on-arrival: garfield_advisor = 1; n_advisors += 1; moderate_strength += 3; moderate_dissent -= 3; workers_rep += 2; rural_rep += 2
go-to: advisor_menu

James Garfield is now an advisor. His broad appeal across factions makes him a valuable unifying figure.

@add_sherman
title: John Sherman
subtitle: Ohio senator and fiscal moderate. Brother of the general. The party's leading voice on economic policy.
is-card: true
card-image: img/portraits/John-Sherman.jpg
tags: moderate_advisor
view-if: sherman_advisor = 0 and n_advisors < 3
on-arrival: sherman_advisor = 1; n_advisors += 1; moderate_strength += 3; moderate_dissent -= 2; middle_class_rep += 3; conservative_dissent -= 2
go-to: advisor_menu

John Sherman is now an advisor. His command of financial policy gives us credibility with the business community.

@add_blaine
title: James Blaine
subtitle: Maine congressman. Ambitious, skilled, and broadly popular.
is-card: true
card-image: img/portraits/James_G._Blaine.jpg
tags: moderate_advisor
view-if: blaine_advisor = 0 and n_advisors < 3
on-arrival: blaine_advisor = 1; n_advisors += 1; moderate_strength += 4; moderate_dissent -= 3; middle_class_rep += 2; rural_rep += 1
go-to: advisor_menu

James Blaine is now an advisor. His national profile and political skill are considerable assets — though his ambition bears watching.

@add_hayes
title: Rutherford Hayes
subtitle: Ohio governor. Moderate, honest, and broadly trusted.
is-card: true
card-image: img/portraits/Rutherford_Hayes.jpg
tags: moderate_advisor
view-if: hayes_advisor = 0 and n_advisors < 3
on-arrival: hayes_advisor = 1; n_advisors += 1; moderate_strength += 3; moderate_dissent -= 2; OH_rural_rep += 3; OH_workers_rep += 2
go-to: advisor_menu

Rutherford Hayes is now an advisor. His reputation for integrity is a useful counterweight to charges of Republican corruption.

@add_fish
title: Hamilton Fish
subtitle: New York moderate. A steady hand on foreign policy.
is-card: true
card-image: img/portraits/Hamilton_Fish.jpg
tags: moderate_advisor
view-if: fish_advisor = 0 and n_advisors < 3
on-arrival: fish_advisor = 1; n_advisors += 1; moderate_strength += 2; moderate_dissent -= 2; europe_relation += 3
go-to: advisor_menu

Hamilton Fish is now an advisor. His diplomatic experience opens doors abroad that would otherwise remain closed.

###################### CONSERVATIVE ADVISORS

@add_conkling
title: Roscoe Conkling
subtitle: New York machine boss and dominant conservative figure. Bitter rival of Blaine. Controls the Custom House.
is-card: true
card-image: img/portraits/Roscoe_Conkling.jpg
tags: conservative_advisor
view-if: conkling_advisor = 0 and n_advisors < 3
on-arrival: conkling_advisor = 1; n_advisors += 1; conservative_strength += 5; conservative_dissent -= 4; resources += 1; liberal_dissent += 3
go-to: advisor_menu

Roscoe Conkling is now an advisor. His machine delivers votes and money — at a price.

@add_cameron
title: Simon Cameron
subtitle: Pennsylvania party boss and former Secretary of War. Old-guard patronage politician.
is-card: true
card-image: img/portraits/Smn_Cameron.jpg
tags: conservative_advisor
view-if: cameron_advisor = 0 and n_advisors < 3
on-arrival: cameron_advisor = 1; n_advisors += 1; conservative_strength += 4; conservative_dissent -= 3; resources += 1; liberal_dissent += 2
go-to: advisor_menu

Simon Cameron is now an advisor. His Pennsylvania machine is a formidable asset, though reformers will complain.

@add_seward
title: William Seward
subtitle: Secretary of State and former Whig leader. Pragmatic conservative and Johnson ally.
is-card: true
card-image: img/portraits/Seward.jpg
tags: conservative_advisor
view-if: seward_advisor = 0 and n_advisors < 3
on-arrival: seward_advisor = 1; n_advisors += 1; conservative_strength += 3; conservative_dissent -= 3; europe_relation += 2; radical_dissent += 3
go-to: advisor_menu

William Seward is now an advisor. His long experience in government is valuable, though the Radicals deeply distrust him.

###################### LIBERAL ADVISORS

@add_schurz
title: Carl Schurz
subtitle: Missouri senator and intellectual leader of the Liberal Republican movement. Champion of civil service reform.
is-card: true
card-image: img/portraits/Schurz,_Hon._Carl.jpg
tags: liberal_advisor
view-if: schurz_advisor = 0 and n_advisors < 3 and liberal_split = 0 
on-arrival: schurz_advisor = 1; n_advisors += 1; liberal_strength += 5; liberal_dissent -= 4; civil_service_reform += 1; middle_class_rep += 2
go-to: advisor_menu

Carl Schurz is now an advisor. His reform credentials and German-American connections are significant assets — but his loyalty to the party is conditional on genuine reform.

@add_trumbull
title: Lyman Trumbull
subtitle: Illinois senator. Voted to acquit Johnson. Drifting steadily toward the Liberal Republicans.
is-card: true
card-image: img/portraits/Lyman_Trumbull.jpg
tags: liberal_advisor
view-if: trumbull_advisor = 0 and n_advisors < 3 and liberal_split = 0
on-arrival: trumbull_advisor = 1; n_advisors += 1; liberal_strength += 3; liberal_dissent -= 3; radical_dissent += 4; moderate_dissent += 2
go-to: advisor_menu

Lyman Trumbull is now an advisor. His legal expertise is valuable, though his vote to acquit Johnson still rankles the Radicals.

@add_cox
title: Jacob Cox
subtitle: Ohio politician and Grant's Interior Secretary. Resigned over civil service disputes. Committed reformer.
is-card: true
card-image: img/portraits/Jacob_Cox.jpg
tags: liberal_advisor
view-if: cox_advisor = 0 and n_advisors < 3 and liberal_split = 0
on-arrival: cox_advisor = 1; n_advisors += 1; liberal_strength += 3; liberal_dissent -= 3; civil_service_reform += 1; conservative_dissent += 2
go-to: advisor_menu

Jacob Cox is now an advisor. His reform credentials are genuine, and his Ohio connections are useful — but he has made enemies within the Grant administration.

###################### NONFACTIONAL ADVISORS

@add_douglass
title: Frederick Douglass
subtitle: The most prominent Black leader in America. His endorsement carries enormous weight with the freedmen community.
is-card: true
card-image: img/portraits/Frederick_Douglass.jpg
tags: nonfactional_advisor
view-if: douglass_advisor = 0 and n_advisors < 3
on-arrival: douglass_advisor = 1; n_advisors += 1; freemen_rep += 5; workers_rep += 2; radical_dissent -= 3; liberal_dissent += 2
go-to: advisor_menu

Frederick Douglass is now an advisor. His moral authority transcends faction — and his connection to the freedmen community is invaluable.